  "detailed_description": "Lumiland is a sokoban-like 3D puzzle game. Adventure through light and shadow, and push the crates to pave the way toward your goal!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Seamless adventure through <strong>over 50 levels</strong><br></li><li>Solving the puzzles by <strong>combining the two characters’ unique abilities</strong><br></li><li>Stylized, delightful art style<br></li><li><strong>Original sound track</strong> by 希望索任合资 (T-L-S)</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characters</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399210/extras/5d9eb68e53baba1b7c50b1ce602c6cc8.avif?t=1613083239\" width=460 height=200 /></span><br>You meet Light first. They walk in the sunlight and like to find new crystal pieces. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399210/extras/e7975b58b3a17bd80b121a4e8e562f41.avif?t=1613083239\" width=460 height=276 /></span><br>There is also Shadow who lives in shadow. Walking in light makes Shadow feel sick, but they can do it if they try hard!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >World</h2><br>In your journey through Lumiland, you will experience five different areas, each with its own art, music, and puzzle styles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399210/extras/93856d8b4496f29ef4db5e42cfad914a.avif?t=1613083239\" width=500 height=299 /></span><br><br>Branching paths provide optional, more-challenging levels to really test your brain.",
  "about_the_game": "Lumiland is a sokoban-like 3D puzzle game. Adventure through light and shadow, and push the crates to pave the way toward your goal!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Seamless adventure through <strong>over 50 levels</strong><br></li><li>Solving the puzzles by <strong>combining the two characters’ unique abilities</strong><br></li><li>Stylized, delightful art style<br></li><li><strong>Original sound track</strong> by 希望索任合资 (T-L-S)</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characters</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399210/extras/5d9eb68e53baba1b7c50b1ce602c6cc8.avif?t=1613083239\" width=460 height=200 /></span><br>You meet Light first. They walk in the sunlight and like to find new crystal pieces. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399210/extras/e7975b58b3a17bd80b121a4e8e562f41.avif?t=1613083239\" width=460 height=276 /></span><br>There is also Shadow who lives in shadow. Walking in light makes Shadow feel sick, but they can do it if they try hard!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >World</h2><br>In your journey through Lumiland, you will experience five different areas, each with its own art, music, and puzzle styles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1399210/extras/93856d8b4496f29ef4db5e42cfad914a.avif?t=1613083239\" width=500 height=299 /></span><br><br>Branching paths provide optional, more-challenging levels to really test your brain.",
